<HEADLINE>
<P>
DISNEY EMPLOYEES AND BEARDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mickey Mouse, Abe Lincoln, Captain Hook, Pluto, Goofy, Walt Disney and the 
Seven Dwarfs: What do they have in common? They have facial hair and they are 
employed in one way or another by Disney. If the amusement industry giant would 
be consistent in its rules, all of these characters should be laid off. What's 
next -- barring admission to their parks and hotels of customers with 
mustaches? What a Goofy, Dopey, Mickey Mouse rule! Where is the ACLU when we 
need it most? 
</P>
<P>
TOM DEITERICH 
</P>
<P>
Ontario 
</P>
</TEXT>
