<HEADLINE>
<P>
'LA TRAVIATA' CAST CHANGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Soprano Stephanie Friede has withdrawn from three performances of Verdi's "La 
Traviata" with Opera Pacific at the Orange County Performing Arts Center. 
Friede, reportedly ill, will be replaced by Brenda Harris at the Sunday matinee 
and by Nova Thomas on Friday and Jan. 21. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011390-0020 </DOCNO>
