<P>
Photo, Cuong Huu Nguyen, left, embraces sister Nga Nguyen Do as brother Tuoi 
Nguyen looks on at Los Angeles airport. ; Photo, Cuong Huu Nguyen, imprisoned 
for 6 1/2 years, hugs unidentified man. LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
