"The most crucial thing for me is the future and the greatness of the Raiders," 
Davis said. "I'm going to do what is best for the team." Wilson said Oakland 
expected to hear something in two weeks, but such optimism has been standard 
among officials meeting with Davis in a bidding process that has been going on 
for 2 1/2 years. 
