<P>
AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; DEFENSE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; 
DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE (U.S.) -- CONTRACTS; DIVESTMENT; FORD AEROSPACE &amp; 
COMMUNICATIONS CORP; FORD MOTOR CO; WEAPONS; ACQUISITIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
