<P>
NELSON SCORES 21 TO LEAD FULLERTON PAST RIVERSIDE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Angie Nelson scored 21 points had nine rebounds to lead Fullerton College to a 
68-48 victory over Riverside in an Orange Empire Conference women's basketball 
game Friday at Fullerton. 
</P>
